---
import Layout from '../../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ARCON Security Solutions">

<main class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen">

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24">

<div class="flex items-center gap-6">

<img src="/logos/arcon.png" class="h-12" alt="ARCON">

<div>

<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400">
ARCON
</h1>

<p class="text-gray-300 mt-2">
Privileged Access Management (PAM) solutions to secure administrative access and critical systems.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Core Products
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• ARCON PAM
</li>
<li>• ARCON Privileged Session Manager
</li>
<li>• ARCON Identity Analytics
</li>
<li>• ARCON Secrets Management
</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Capabilities
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• Privileged account discovery and onboarding</li>
<li>• Session monitoring and recording</li>
<li>• Least-privilege enforcement</li>
<li>• Credential vaulting and rotation</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Use Cases
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• Securing administrative access to critical systems</li>
<li>• Recording and auditing privileged sessions</li>
<li>• Enforcing least-privilege across IT and OT systems</li>
<li>• Managing secrets for automated workflows</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Why ARCON
</h2>

<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
ARCON delivers enterprise-grade PAM with rich session monitoring and analytics to reduce insider and external privileged risk.
</p>

</div>

</section>

</main>

</Layout>
